# Step 4: Buying on credit
# Instead of paying cash, farmer extends credit (a liability)

2024-01-01 * Investor puts cash into business
  Equity:Input -> Asset:Cash investment 25.00 GBP

2024-01-02 * Buy oranges on credit from farmer
  Liability:Farmer -> Expense:Purchases oranges on credit 25.00 GBP

2024-01-03 * Sell oranges at market
  Income:Sales -> Asset:Cash market sales 37.50 GBP
